== Records ==

=== NFL records ===

* Most games with 4+ touchdowns: 6
* Most seasons averaging 100+ yards per game: 7

* Most seasons leading the NFL in rushing yards: 8

* Consecutive seasons leading the NFL in rushing yards: 5

* Most seasons leading the NFL in rushing touchdowns: 5

* Tied with Steve Van Buren and Leroy Kelly for most consecutive seasons leading the NFL in rushing touchdowns: 3

* Fewest games to reach 12,000 career rushing yards: 115

* Career rushing yards per game: 104.3

* Career rushing yards per attempt by a running back (minimum 1,500 carries): 5.22

* Yards per carry in a season (minimum 200 attempts): 6.4

=== Browns franchise records ===

* Rushing touchdowns: 106

* Rushing yards: 12,312

* Combined net yards: 15,459

* Career touchdowns: 126

* 1,000+ yard seasons: 7

* Consecutive games scoring a touchdown: 10

* Points in a season: 126

* Rushing yards in a season: 1,863

* Rushing touchdowns in a season: 17 (twice)

